In the showroom there was 170cm of space between the 3seater sofa and the kitchen edge which was along the length (longer side) of the dining area
The reduction in size is 4.40-3.93 = 0.47m so the space for a desk is 170cm-47cm = 123cm (for reference my current desk in Englishcombe is 104cm and just about holds my laptop+monitor)

